Last Broadcast Date: Thu 10 Feb 2011
Mark Henderson In 2003, a backpacking trip to Colombia turned into a three month ordeal for Mark Henderson when he was kidnapped by left wing guerrillas. After his release, he returned to the UK, but nearly a year later he was emailed by one of his kidnappers. Mark tells the story of his captivity, and his subsequent meeting with two of the people who had kidnapped him. Show less